{"id":"helah","term":"Helah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Rust, (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 4:5\">1 Chr. 4:5</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 4:7\">7</a>), one of the wives of Ashur.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 4:5","1 Chronicles 4:7"]}